                "text": "Let's solve the equation:\n\n\\[\n\\sin(x) + x^2 = 42\n\\]\n\nThis is a nonlinear equation and cannot be solved analytically, but we can use numerical methods to find the solution. Let's find its solution(s) numerically.",
